'''热带风暴阿琳'''（{{lang-en|Tropical Storm Arlene}}）是1981年5月吹袭[[古巴|古巴]]和[[巴哈马|巴哈马]]的一场较为罕见的[[淡季大西洋热带气旋列表|淡季]][[热带气旋|热带气旋]]。系统的源头就非同寻常，是从东太平洋进入[[加勒比海|加勒比海]]的[[热带扰动|热带扰动]]，历史上很少有[[北大西洋热带气旋|北大西洋热带气旋]]由此途径生成。5月6日，系统发展成热带低气压，并于次日在[[开曼群岛|开曼群岛]]附近升级成热带风暴并获名“阿琳”，此时距这年[[大西洋飓风季|大西洋飓风季]]正式开始还有超过三周时间。阿琳也是1970年的[[1970年飓风阿尔玛|飓风阿尔玛]]之后首场5月大西洋热带风暴。

气旋存在期间总体保持向东北方向移动，经过古巴和巴哈马东南部时产生降雨和局部阵风。5月9日，阿琳被规模更大但不具备热带天气系统特征的风暴吸收而消散。没有任何报导表明系统曾造成人员丧生或重大破坏。

== 气象历史 ==
{{storm path|Arlene 1981 track.png}}
热带风暴阿琳源自1981年5月上旬东太平洋发展出的云系，系统穿越[[中美洲|中美洲]]，到5月5日下午已在[[洪都拉斯|洪都拉斯]]近海的[[罗阿坦岛|罗阿坦岛]]附近发展出下层环流。系统内的[[对流|对流]]起初杂乱无章，所以气象机构没有将之归类成[[热带气旋|热带气旋]]。5月6日晚，[[国家飓风中心|美国国家飓风中心]]开始通过[[德沃夏克分析法|德沃夏克分析法]]估算系统强度，<ref name="lushine">{{cite report | author = [[国家飓风中心|National Hurricane Center]] | publisher = [[美国国家海洋和大气管理局|National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration]] | year = 1981 | title = Summary on Tropical Storm Arlene | accessdate = 2016-05-09 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/cdmp/dvd0115-jpg/1981/atlantic/arlene/postevent/arlene1981.jpg | location = [[迈阿密|Miami]], [[佛罗里达州|FL]] | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | format = [[JPEG|JPG]] | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303194320/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/cdmp/dvd0115-jpg/1981/atlantic/arlene/postevent/arlene1981.jpg | date =  }}</ref>结果表明系统已在[[开曼群岛|开曼群岛]]附近成为热带低气压<ref name="HURDAT">{{cite report | author = Hurricane Research Division | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | year = 2009 | accessdate = 2016-05-09 | title = Easy-to-Read HURDAT 1851–2008 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160305031132/http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/hurdat/easyread-2009.html | archivedate = 2016-03-05 | url = http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/hurdat/easyread-2009.html | date =  }}</ref>。历史上还很少有[[北大西洋热带气旋|北大西洋热带气旋]]是经东太平洋的[[热带扰动|扰动天气]]发展而成<ref name="tcr">{{cite report | author = National Hurricane Center | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | year = 1981 | title = Tropical Storm Arlene Preliminary Report | accessdate = 2010-01-03 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1981-prelim/arlene/prelim01.gif | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303220115/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1981-prelim/arlene/prelim01.gif | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | format = [[GIF|GIF]] | location = Miami, FL | date =  | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

成为热带气旋后，系统迅速发展，环流周围形成螺旋状雨带。5月7日，美国国家飓风中心根据卫星图像把气旋升级成热带风暴，并以“阿琳”（{{lang|en|Arlene}}）命名。此后不久，[[飓风猎人|飓风猎人]]侦察机确认系统达到热带风暴标准，并测得1000[[巴|毫巴]]（[[帕斯卡|百帕]]，29.53[[英寸汞柱|英寸汞柱]]）[[气压|气压]]值。此后直至消散，风暴环流都位于深层对流的西部边缘。<ref name="lushine" />阿琳之后略有强化，风速提升至每小时85公里，然后于5月8日清晨从[[古巴|古巴]]东部上岸<ref name="HURDAT" />。逼近陆地期间，气旋的对流逐渐减弱，其中心在北侧的[[高气压|高气压天气系统]]影响下稳步向东北方向前进<ref>{{cite report | author = National Hurricane Center | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | year = 1981 | title = Tropical Storm Arlene Discussion | accessdate = 2016-05-10 | archivedate = 2012-10-23 | location = Miami, FL | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121023235456/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/cdmp/dvd0115-jpg/1981/atlantic/arlene/tropdisc/tcd05080300z.jpg | deadurl = no | format = JPG | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/cdmp/dvd0115-jpg/1981/atlantic/arlene/tropdisc/tcd05080300z.jpg | date =  }}</ref>。

途经古巴东部期间，阿琳的环流变得混乱，不过气象机构估计系统有可能会在返回海洋上空后重组<ref>{{cite report | author = National Hurricane Center | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | year = 1981 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303200225/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/cdmp/dvd0115-jpg/1981/atlantic/arlene/tropdisc/tcd05080900z.jpg | title = Tropical Storm Arlene Discussion | accessdate = 2016-05-10 | deadurl = no | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/cdmp/dvd0115-jpg/1981/atlantic/arlene/tropdisc/tcd05080900z.jpg | format = JPG | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | date =  }}</ref>。抵达开放水域上空时，气旋强度已降至热带低气压标准，并且对流在强烈风切变的影响下向中心以东严重偏移，美国国家飓风中心估计系统不大可能会重新发展强化<ref name="tcr" /><ref>{{cite report | author = National Hurricane Center | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | year = 1981 | title = Tropical Storm Arlene Discussion | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/cdmp/dvd0115-jpg/1981/atlantic/arlene/tropdisc/tcd05081500z.jpg | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2016-05-10 | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | format = JPG | location = Miami, FL | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303185932/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/cdmp/dvd0115-jpg/1981/atlantic/arlene/tropdisc/tcd05081500z.jpg | date =  }}</ref>。但是，[[美国国家海洋和大气管理局|美国国家海洋和大气管理局]]所派侦察机还是测得阿琳的风速短暂提升到每小时95公里，此时风暴正位于巴哈马东南部上空，中心向外延伸出大规模的对流带。[[雷暴|雷暴]]活动消散后，气旋风速再度下降，阿琳的强度回落到热带低气压水平。5月9日清晨，系统被逐渐逼近的低压槽吸收。<ref name="tcr" />次日夜间，合并而成的新系统经重新组织发展出类似[[亚热带气旋|亚热带天气系统]]的特征，再于5月11日进一步弱化<ref name="lushine" />。

== 防灾措施和影响 ==
美国国家飓风中心在阿琳首度[[登陆_(气象学)|登陆]]前发布公告，称[[牙买加|牙买加]]、古巴和巴哈马可能降下暴雨，并建议相应地区的小型船只留在港口，不要出海。巴哈马政府在此期间向该国中部及东南部发布[[暴雨警告|暴雨警告]]。<ref>{{cite report | author = National Hurricane Center | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | year = 1981 | title = Tropical Storm Arlene Advisory 2 | accessdate = 2016-05-10 | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303231947/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/cdmp/dvd0115-jpg/1981/atlantic/arlene/public/pub05072200z.jpg | format = JPG | location = Miami, FL | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/cdmp/dvd0115-jpg/1981/atlantic/arlene/public/pub05072200z.jpg | date =  }}</ref>没有任何报导表明古巴或巴哈马因这场风暴导致人员伤亡或破坏，因此气旋的整体影响很小<ref name="tcr" />。阿琳经过期间，[[开曼布拉克|开曼布拉克]]测得时速74公里的大风<ref>{{cite report | author = National Hurricane Center | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | year = 1981 | title = Reports from Cayman Brac | accessdate = 2016-05-10 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/cdmp/dvd0115-jpg/1981/atlantic/arlene/sfcdat/hw.jpg | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121023235531/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/cdmp/dvd0115-jpg/1981/atlantic/arlene/sfcdat/hw.jpg | archivedate = 2012-10-23 | location = Miami, FL | deadurl = no | format = JPG | date =  }}</ref>，此后巴哈马测得的最强风速约为每小时56公里<ref>{{cite report | author = National Hurricane Center | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | year = 1981 | title = Reports from the Bahamas | accessdate = 2016-05-10 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303204647/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/cdmp/dvd0115-jpg/1981/atlantic/arlene/sfcdat/hwbahamas.jpg | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | deadurl = no | location = Miami, FL | format = JPG | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/cdmp/dvd0115-jpg/1981/atlantic/arlene/sfcdat/hwbahamas.jpg | date =  }}</ref>。截至2015年，阿琳仍然是有纪录以来唯一在5月对古巴[[卡马圭省|卡马圭省]]构成影响的热带风暴，但这些影响总体而言仅限于扰乱甘蔗生产<ref>{{cite web | author = Academia de Ciencia de Cuba/Centro Meteorológico Camaguey | date = 1994-12-03 | title = Ciclones tropicales y produccion agricola.Prejuicios y beneficios | accessdate = 2016-05-10 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303182411/http://www.cbmet.com/cbm-files/20-4ad48b3cfa9347b2efa5b4f8af8d6442.DOC | url = http://www.cbmet.com/cbm-files/20-4ad48b3cfa9347b2efa5b4f8af8d6442.DOC | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | format = [[DOC格式|DOC]] | df =  }}</ref>。

